Class DoubleStack

    @Generated(date="2017-10-22T12:31:11+0200",
           value="KTypeStack.java")
public class DoubleStack
extends DoubleArrayList
    A subclass of DoubleArrayList adding stack-related utility methods. The top of the stack is at the DoubleArrayList.size() - 1 element.
